{
  "stem": "15943.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I always think of him as Prince Charming in the fairy tale who came on a white horse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he became hysterical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[CRYING] [DRINKS] He said we were the first Jewish girls he found alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[CRYING] And he started telling us what he found.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think at that point, we were ready to give up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But somehow, you, you bounce back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Skin and bones, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] skin and bones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had my-- I knew that my sisters and brother went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So being very naive as far as Russia goes at that point, we figured we'll go to Russia to find them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first I said to Carol-- today I call her Carol.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We called her Karola.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were two other girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just looked at the picture in the album.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I spoke to one a couple of weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's go to the Russian-- meet the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were transports of Russian people-- of slave laborers that were sent there from Russia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we'll go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we'll find our-- my families.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we'll have somebody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't know if you went to Russia, you never came back out of Russia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that time, we didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we decided to make-- after we found out by meeting Russian soldiers that we can't go to Russia because we're not Russians.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't tell us that you don't come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, Russia is a big country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're not going to find your family there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided to make our way back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were on foot for three weeks, the four girls hiding in empty houses.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
